{"tid":1919850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"波蘭軍方高級將領確診武漢肺炎   曾赴德參加軍事會議","createTime":"2020-03-11T05:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T07:11:50.000Z","uid":67454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7f43a875301a81740155ef3f8d8769bbe7ee9f8c","tid":1919850,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"（中央社華沙10日綜合外電報導）波蘭國防部今天表示，波蘭武裝部隊總司令部指揮官米卡（Jaroslaw Mika）將軍自德國返回後，確診感染2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）。<br />\n<br />\n波蘭國防部推特說，在德國參加軍事會議返國後，米卡將軍經診斷確認感染武漢肺炎，隨行十多名人員已接受隔離檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n推文指出，米卡將軍目前狀態良好。（譯者：徐崇哲）1090310<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202003100470.aspx?fbclid=IwAR0w89ZnppVS3ev5b-HY5-pSBZUP8PQsDL8704bsYTR1T8agsvaJD5-YE44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202003100470.aspx%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0w89ZnppVS3ev5b-HY5-pSBZUP8PQsDL8704bsYTR1T8agsvaJD5-YE44&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPWWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=8fe0afee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202003100470.aspx?fbclid=IwAR0w89ZnppVS3ev5b-HY5-pSBZUP8PQsDL8704bsYTR1T8agsvaJD5-YE44</a>"},{"pid":"3fdd2feb39604234fd6a0afdb1fcd6e029b1b81d","tid":1919850,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:06:09.000Z","msg":"正 直接攻頂 <br />\n<br />\n總司令傳比幾個副司令<br />\n副司令再傳比幾個助理司令<br />\n一層傳下一層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4585ffd5ca32cf4c28dd66cebd973ce7915a91f5","tid":1919850,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa1a40ebacfe5f1c1d4bf74472b01da2e0ba639","tid":1919850,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"kurwa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\"